-我告诉他了  -什么
- I told him. - What?!

191
00:14:07,610 --> 00:14:09,790
他好像已经知道了似的
It's like he already knew!

192
00:14:11,110 --> 00:14:12,690
你说什么了吗
Did you say something?

193
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:14,980
我从没对任何人说起
I never said anything to anyone!

194
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,790
那他是怎么知道的
Then how did he already know?

195
00:14:20,270 --> 00:14:21,400
他在哪
Where is he?

196
00:14:27,170 --> 00:14:29,430
-你只会越描越黑  -我得试着
- You'll only make it worse. - I have to try

197
00:14:29,570 --> 00:14:31,310
跟他解释
and explain to him.

198
00:14:31,730 --> 00:14:34,270
你能说什么啊
What could you possibly say?

199
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:39,360
说不是你的错  我强迫你的
That it wasn't your doing; I pressured you.

200
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:41,200
可那不是真的
That's not true.

201
00:14:41,610 --> 00:14:43,610
我不能回避他
I can't avoid him.

202
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:46,610
他是我的朋友  我的护卫
He's my friend, my champion.

203
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,590
我们当初为何要那么做啊
Why did we ever do it?

204
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:54,260
里昂提斯是个好人
Leontes is a good man.

205
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:56,680
不会有事的
It'll be all right.

206
00:14:57,570 --> 00:14:59,050
会的
It won't.

207
00:15:08,870 --> 00:15:10,790
-她在干嘛  -在练习
- What's she doing? - She's practicing.

208
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:11,710
练习什么
Practicing what?

209
00:15:11,850 --> 00:15:14,700
-自控能力  -这能有什么用
- Self control. - How will that help us?

210
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:16,490
我们绑架了国王的母亲
We kidnapped the king's mother.

211
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:19,630
