Your fear is useless to Morgan.

212
00:15:19,770 --> 00:15:22,130
要么相信她  要么就走人
Giver her your faith or nothing at all.

213
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:24,160
但总会有报应的
But surely there will be retribution.

214
00:15:24,310 --> 00:15:27,260
会的  所以我们要团结一致
There will be, and we must stand firm.

215
00:15:27,530 --> 00:15:30,420
国王的母亲已经疯了
The king's mother has gone mad.

216
00:15:30,560 --> 00:15:33,440
梅林孤掌难鸣了
Merlin is acting alone.

217
00:15:33,570 --> 00:15:34,790
懂吗
Understand?

218
00:15:39,660 --> 00:15:42,590
你见到国王的话  让他来找我
You see the king, you tell him to come and find me.

219
00:15:42,690 --> 00:15:44,680
找到我前  不要让别人跟他说话
No one is to speak to him before I do.

220
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:46,850
-懂吗  -是
- Understand? - Right.

221
00:15:48,780 --> 00:15:50,270
我知道他们彼此喜欢
I knew that they had eyes for each other,

222
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:52,130
但我不知道都到了这种程度
but I had no idea it had got to this.

223
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:53,790
可摩根却发现了
But Morgan did.

224
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:56,490
我需要你帮我摆平此事
I need your help to put this right.

225
00:15:56,750 --> 00:16:00,060
这里的人仰仗你  向你吐露心声
People here rely on you, confide in you.

226
00:16:00,210 --> 00:16:02,310
他们把你视作指引
They look to you as their guide.

227
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:05,200
那我该怎么做
Well, what can I do?

228
00:16:05,350 --> 00:16:07,420
其他人绝不能知道此事
The men must never find out about this.

229
00:16:07,570 --> 00:16:09,260
他们都会觉得受到了背叛
They'll all feel betrayed.

230
00:16:09,410 --> 00:16:13,420
让桂妮维尔冷静  千万别乱说
Keep Guinevere under control and quiet.

231
00:16:15,430 --> 00:16:16,780
那摩根呢
What about Morgan?

232
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:18,730
我会去找她的
Oh, I'll get to her.

233
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:21,380
但得先找到亚瑟
I have to find Arthur first.

234
00:16:21,530 --> 00:16:23,870
我所有的努力  又有人阻碍我的计划
All I've worked for, and it's people who get in the way again.

235
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:25,190
坏事的总是人
Always people.

236
00:16:25,330 --> 00:16:26,490
我要见国王
I need to speak to the king.

237
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:28,650
-怎么回事  -我的家人需要帮助
- What's the trouble here? - My family need his help.

238
00:16:28,790 --> 00:16:30,060
国王现在不能见你
The king can't see you now.

239
00:16:30,210 --> 00:16:31,350
我要和他说话
I need to speak to him!

240
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:32,830
像其他人一样等着
Wait your turn like everyone else.

241
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:41,510
卡米洛特在垂死挣扎呢
Camelot is in its death throes.

242
00:16:41,670 --> 00:16:44,090
一旦谎言被揭穿
Once its lies are exposed,

243
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:46,150
