Once, you said.

260
00:18:24,730 --> 00:18:26,820
我怎么知道你没撒谎呢
How do I know you're telling me the truth?

261
00:18:26,970 --> 00:18:27,930
你父亲过世的时候
It happened again on the journey

262
00:18:28,050 --> 00:18:29,200
