I know what I did was wrong.

267
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:43,430
我只求你的原谅
I'm just asking you to forgive me.

268
00:18:45,890 --> 00:18:48,780
我也想  但我做不到
And I want to, but I don't know how to.

269
00:18:48,910 --> 00:18:50,730
我配不上你
I don't deserve you.

270
00:19:01,050 --> 00:19:04,470
你早上为何会问起
What made you ask me this morning?

271
