It was something Igraine said.

272
00:19:10,320 --> 00:19:12,370
伊格兰
Igraine...

273
00:19:12,530 --> 00:19:14,670
她说什么了
What did she say?

274
00:19:16,170 --> 00:19:19,240
我要是不问你  你会说吗
If I hadn't have asked you, would you have told me?

275
00:19:20,860 --> 00:19:23,140
我宁可撒谎
I'd rather lie,

276
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:26,100
活在愧疚当中
and live with my guilt

277
00:19:27,490 --> 00:19:29,540
也不愿伤害你
than ever hurt you.

278
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:38,020
我宁愿你不要撒谎
And I would rather you do anything than lie to me.

279
00:19:51,330 --> 00:19:53,050
你该告诉我的
You should have told me.

280
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,640
我发过誓不会背叛她  不会背叛任何人
I swore I'd never betray her or anyone else.

281
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:57,430
所以你甚至不打算抵赖了
So you're not even gonna try and deny it.

282
00:19:57,540 --> 00:19:59,180
不  这是事实
No. It's the truth.

283
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:02,680
永远不要向这里的其他人承认  懂吗
Never admit that to anyon else here. Understand?

284
00:20:02,830 --> 00:20:05,120
不是那么简单的事  我伤了我在乎的人
It's not that easy. I've hurt people I care about.

285
00:20:05,260 --> 00:20:07,840
那些人无关要紧  你是国王
Those people don't matter! You're a king.

286
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:11,490
你只要对你的领土负责  别的不管
Your responsibility is to your realm! Nothing more.

287
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:14,930
那你要我怎么做
So what do you suggest I do?

288
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:20,530
要么掩盖此事
Cover this up,

289
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:23,460
要么就准备好失去一切
or risk losing everything.

290
00:20:23,600 --> 00:20:25,210
我必须要跟国王说话
I must speak to the king!

291
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:27,060
你是什么人
Who the hell are you?

292
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:30,040
-陛下  求您  -你有何事
- Your Majesty, please! - What do you want?

293
00:20:30,150 --> 00:20:33,040
我家人在巴尔东被包围了
My family is under siege at Bardon Pass.

294
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:41,540
你叫什么
What's your name?

295
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:44,640
阿尔比恩  陛下
Albion, Majesty.

296
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:48,000
我父亲  他派我来告诉您
My father, he sent me to tell you

297
00:20:48,120 --> 00:20:50,290
有人在袭击巴尔东
that men are attacking Bardon Pass.

298
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:53,560
必须保卫巴尔东
The Bardon Pass has to be defended.

299
00:20:55,220 --> 00:20:57,550
让大家集合
I want the men assembled now.

300
00:20:57,800 --> 00:21:00,600
巴尔东是进入卡米洛特主要商道
Bardon Pass is the main trade route into Camelot.

301
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:04,480
若失去这条路  大家就会说我们软弱
If we lose that, word wil spread of our weakness,

302
00:21:04,610 --> 00:21:06,870
我们的领土就会受到威胁
and all our land could come under threat.

303
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,250
我们要保护那家人  保护我们的领地
We protect the family and our territory.

304
00:21:09,370 --> 00:21:11,650
不能有任何妥协
Nothing less is acceptable.

305
00:21:12,790 --> 00:21:14,410
怎么不见里昂提斯
Where's Leontes?

306
00:21:19,890 --> 00:21:21,750
巴尔东受袭
Bardon Pass is under attack.

307
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:23,770
你的人需要你
Your men need you.

308
00:21:23,930 --> 00:21:25,420
我要回家  回我的村子去
I'm going home to my village.

309
00:21:25,570 --> 00:21:29,280
这里就是你的家  我们是你的家人
This is your home. We are your family.

310
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:32,580
履行你对国王的誓言
Fulfil your oath to your king,

311
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:35,940
否则你的荣誉将毁于一旦
or your honour counts for nothing.

312
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:37,770
跟国王说所谓的荣誉去吧
You talk to the king of honour.

313
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:39,830
他玷污了我的新娘
He fucked my bride.

314
00:21:39,970 --> 00:21:43,140
此事了结  亚瑟会承担责任
And Arthur will be held to account when this is over.

315
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:45,930
但是现在我们有危机要处理
But right now we have a crisis on our hands,

316
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:49,660
你对你的人有一份责任
and you have a duty to your men.

317
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:53,370
等我回来
When I return,

318
00:21:53,610 --> 00:21:56,090
就与卡米洛特一刀两断
I'm done with Camelot.

319
00:21:57,340 --> 00:22:02,240
那要由你和你妻子来决定了
That's for you and your wife to decide.

320
00:22:02,890 --> 00:22:04,980
桂妮维尔  让他去吧
Guinevere! Leave the men be!

321
00:22:05,110 --> 00:22:07,320
你觉得我凭什么还会听你的
What makes you think I'm ever going to listen to you again?

322
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:09,750
我告诉过你离他远点  你没听我的
I told you to stay away from him, but you didn't listen to me.

323
00:22:09,890 --> 00:22:12,270
所以你就告诉里昂提斯我背叛他了
So you tell Leontes I betrayed him?

324
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:15,100
-我什么都没说  -只有你知道
- No, I didn't say anything. - You are the only one who knew.

325
00:22:15,230 --> 00:22:17,420
桂妮维尔  请听我说
Guinevere, please,

326
00:22:17,570 --> 00:22:19,590
这里发生的诡异之事
there are things that have gone on here that are far,

327
00:22:19,710 --> 00:22:22,350
远超你的想象
far more wicked than anything that you have done.

328
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:24,960
有时间时我会解释的
In time I will explain.

329
00:22:28,260 --> 00:22:30,730
里昂提斯忘带他的祈祷书了
Leontes forgot his prayer book.

330
00:22:30,860 --> 00:22:32,650
他上战场总是带着的
He never goes to battle without it.

331
00:22:32,800 --> 00:22:34,430
你真的觉得
Do you really think

332
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:37,230
他现在会想见你吗
that he wants to see you now?

333
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:42,860
只有那一次
It was once.

334
00:22:43,130 --> 00:22:45,800
只有一次啊
Only once.

335
