高文
Gawain...

338
00:23:05,360 --> 00:23:07,540
别让国王离开你的视线
Never let the king out of your sight.

339
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:10,480
要是里昂提斯企图伤害亚瑟  就阻止他
If Leontes moves to hurt Arthur, step in.

340
00:23:10,480 --> 00:23:11,990
里昂提斯
Leontes?

341
00:23:12,110 --> 00:23:14,360
现在别质疑我的话
Don't question me. Not now.

342
00:23:14,490 --> 00:23:17,440
要是他或者任何人要伤害国王
If he or anyone else makes to harm the king,

343
00:23:17,550 --> 00:23:19,850
你要做你该做的
do what you have to do.

344
00:23:19,990 --> 00:23:23,480
笑一笑  装得像我刚讲了个笑话
Now, smile, like I've taught you a joke.

345
00:23:24,770 --> 00:23:26,750
好了  我们走
All right, let's move!

346
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:31,870
胜利归来
Be victorious!

347
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:34,280
-为了卡米洛特  -为了卡米洛特
- For Camelot! - For Camelot!

348
00:23:34,390 --> 00:23:35,800
为了卡米洛特
For Camelot!

349
00:23:40,520 --> 00:23:43,710
现在商道全无安全可言
The trade routes are now completely unsafe!

350
00:23:43,850 --> 00:23:45,660
国王的旗帜毫无效力
The banner of the king means nothing!

351
00:23:45,790 --> 00:23:47,460
先生们  拜托
Gentlemen, please!

352
00:23:47,600 --> 00:23:48,920
求你们
Please.

353
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,860
要对我弟弟有信心
We must have faith in my brother.

354
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:53,710
信任替代不了信心
Faith is no substitute for real confidence!

355
00:23:53,850 --> 00:23:55,860
我绝不会背叛亚瑟
I will not heed disloyalty against Arthur.

356
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:56,790
那不是他的错
It's not his fault

357
